    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing service and subframe reinforcement have been professionally completed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers for enhanced turn-in response without sacrificing streetability. Impeccable paint depth and a pristine interior reflect its pampered history. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
