    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this meticulously maintained masterpiece. This vehicle presents in true showroom condition, boasting a deep, glass-like finish on its original factory paint, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Every body panel is laser-straight, free from even the smallest stone chips or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a thick binder of records documenting its pampered life. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage reflects its history as a garage-kept, fair-weather-only vehicle. Equipped with brand-new premium tires and featuring pristine alloy wheels with zero curb rash, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example that requires absolutely nothing but a new driver.",
